title: 8-9am- Al Green & the Keys to Good Sleep

description: 48 years ago today Al Green quit the music business after a crazy incident with an ex girlfriend, members of BTS have to do military service, we learn about the Korean War, The Rock and Kelly Clarkson do a tribute to Loretta Lynn, Carrie Underwood rocks out to Gunz N Roses, some fast facts, things that young adults think their parent’s generation got right, the keys to getting good sleep, do not read The Gray Man books before bed, and Vinnie reads your texts!
